<h1 class="p-3 mx-5">Nutritionest FAQ</h1>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">🤷‍♀️ What is Nutritionest?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Nutritionest is a web application designed to help users make informed decisions about the foods they eat. It uses the Nutritionix API to provide detailed nutritional information for thousands of different food items.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">⚙️ How does Nutritionest work?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">To use Nutritionest, simply enter a search term for the food you're interested in. Our application will show you a list of 20 different food items that match your search. From there, you can click on any of the items to see detailed nutritional information, such as the amount of fat, protein, and fiber in a 100g serving.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">✅ Can I save my favorite food items on Nutritionest?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Yes! With Nutritionest, you can create your own profile and save lists of your favorite food items. This makes it easy to reference the nutritional information for the foods you eat regularly.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">🫶 Is Nutritionest free to use?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Yes, Nutritionest is completely free to use.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">👥 Who created Nutritionest?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Nutritionest was created by a Berlin-based team passionate about nutrition and technology.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">🎯 How accurate is the nutritional information provided by Nutritionest?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Nutritionest uses the Nutritionix API, which is known for its accuracy and reliability in providing nutritional information.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">🙋 Can I suggest a food item to be added to the Nutritionest database?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">Unfortunately, at this time, we are not accepting suggestions for new food items to be added to the database.</p>

	<h2 class="fs-3 p-3 mx-5">📬 Where can I get support for Nutritionest?</h2>
	<p class="fs-4 p-3 mx-5">You can contact us through our website's contact page for any issues or questions you may have about Nutritionest. Thank you for using Nutritionest!</p>
